            <link>https://justnow.tk.sg</link>
            <sparkle:fullReleaseNotesLink>https://justnow.tk.sg/releases/</sparkle:fullReleaseNotesLink>
            <sparkle:version>10</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.3.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown">- Added indexed full-history search in the rewind overlay so you can find retained screen text without scrubbing frame by frame.
- Added in-frame search match highlighting to make matched words easier to spot once a result is open.
- Added clickable overlay controls for close, previous/next frame, and search.
- Added a configurable pause/resume shortcut and improved pause state visibility in the menu bar.
- Smoothed search and scrolling transitions in the rewind overlay.
</description>
